{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":757,"text":"Five hundred seventy-one million"},{"time":4244,"text":"two hundred thirty thousand pounds of paper towels"},{"time":10551,"text":"are used by Americans"},{"time":12438,"text":"every year."},{"time":16109,"text":"If we could -- correction, wrong figure --"},{"time":19164,"text":"13 billion used every year."},{"time":21515,"text":"If we could reduce the usage of paper towels,"},{"time":24618,"text":"one paper towel per person per day,"},{"time":27800,"text":"571,230,000 pounds of paper not used."},{"time":34681,"text":"We can do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36816,"text":"Now there are all kinds of paper towel dispensers."},{"time":40746,"text":"There's the tri-fold. People typically take two or three."},{"time":44977,"text":"There's the one that cuts it, that you have to tear off."},{"time":49140,"text":"People go one, two, three, four, tear."},{"time":51404,"text":"This much, right?"},{"time":52842,"text":"There's the one that cuts itself."},{"time":55307,"text":"People go, one, two, three, four."},{"time":59447,"text":"Or there's the same thing, but recycled paper,"},{"time":63522,"text":"you have to get five of those because they're not as absorbent, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68035,"text":"The fact is, you can do it all with one towel."},{"time":74556,"text":"The key, two words:"},{"time":76596,"text":"This half of the room, your word is \"shake.\""},{"time":81044,"text":"Let's hear it. Shake. Louder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83226,"text":"Audience: Shake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84771,"text":"Joe Smith: Your word is \"fold.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":86947,"text":"Audience: Fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88063,"text":"JS: Again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88990,"text":"Audience: Fold. JS: Really loud."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91059,"text":"Audience: Shake. Fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92607,"text":"JS: OK. Wet hands."},{"time":96767,"text":"Shake -- one, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, 10, 11, 12."},{"time":101567,"text":"Why 12? Twelve apostles, twelve tribes,"},{"time":104505,"text":"twelve zodiac signs, twelve months. The one I like the best:"},{"time":108612,"text":"It's the biggest number with one syllable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110809,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115071,"text":"Tri-fold. Fold ..."},{"time":122431,"text":"Dry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123983,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128215,"text":"Audience: Shake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133429,"text":"Fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136361,"text":"JS: Cuts itself. Fold. The fold is important"},{"time":138939,"text":"because it allows interstitial suspension."},{"time":143821,"text":"You don't have to remember that part, but trust me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146299,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":151352,"text":"Audience: Shake. Fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158069,"text":"JS: Cuts itself."},{"time":163731,"text":"You know the funny thing is,"},{"time":164888,"text":"I get my hands drier than people do with three or four,"},{"time":167063,"text":"because they can't get in between the cracks."},{"time":169511,"text":"If you think this isn't as good..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172655,"text":"Audience: Shake. Fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181124,"text":"JS: Now, there's now a real fancy invention,"},{"time":184692,"text":"it's the one where you wave your hand"},{"time":187099,"text":"and it kicks it out."},{"time":188890,"text":"It's way too big a towel."},{"time":190976,"text":"Let me tell you a secret."},{"time":192003,"text":"If you're really quick, if you're really quick --"},{"time":194090,"text":"and I can prove this --"},{"time":195670,"text":"this is half a towel from the dispenser in this building."},{"time":200519,"text":"How? As soon as it starts, you just tear it off."},{"time":203886,"text":"It's smart enough to stop."},{"time":205558,"text":"And you get half a towel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209550,"text":"Audience: Shake. Fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222827,"text":"JS: Now, let's all say it together. Shake. Fold."},{"time":229661,"text":"You will for the rest of your life remember those words"},{"time":233804,"text":"every time you pick up a paper towel."},{"time":236787,"text":"And remember, one towel per person for one year --"},{"time":241875,"text":"571,230,000 pounds of paper. No small thing."},{"time":246595,"text":"And next year, toilet paper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248843,"text":"(Laughter)"}]}]}